SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       The full documentation for ppiinnkkyy is
       maintained as a Texinfo manual.  If the  iinnffoo
       and  ppiinnkkyy programs are properly installed
       at your site, the command

              iinnffoo ppiinnkkyy

       should give you access to the complete manual.



pinky 6.7                        December 2006
